<figureCitation id="1F9C2A11910D595CAB50DF5B2183FD95" box="[1141,1220,538,563]" captionStart="Figures 12-22" captionStartId="7.[94,162,2010,2035]" captionTargetBox="[113,1398,204,1980]" captionTargetId="figure-1@7.[113,1398,204,1980]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="Figures 12-22. (12) Blabicentrus lineatus, female, dorsal habitus; (13) Pseudestola densepunctata, female, dorsal habitus; (14) Proceroblesthis prolata, male, dorsal habitus; (15) Butocrysa insignis, male, dorsal habitus; (16) Phoebella albomaculata, male, dorsal habitus; (17) Rhaphiptera affinis, male, dorsal habitus; (18) Desmiphora(Desmiphora) cirrosa, female,dorsal habitus;(19) Cipriscola fasciata, male,dorsal habitus.(20-21) Metacriodioncapixaba,female:(20)dorsal view; (21) ventral view;(22) Eriphusmexicanus, female,dorsal view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4614843" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4614843/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Fig. 22</figureCitation>
